Title: Fifty Tons
Plot: After the murder of an ICE agent in Mexico, LPD is on high alert. Sifuentes is determined to hit the cartels where it hurts, and a local casino's connection to a prostitution ring may give him the chance he needs. The investigation leads to a warehouse and a hidden find that these narcotics cops have never seen before.
ParentalRatingReason: Lightbox Provisional Classification. Official NZ Rating To Be Confirmed.
